Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:09.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:20.16,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:53.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.55,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:07.02,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:14.33,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:21.03,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:28.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm unsure too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:53.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,About being a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,About going into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether those are\Nthe right things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I are completely\Ndifferent in every respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:07.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're alike in just one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hurry up\Nto the left flight deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Hurry!\N— All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our Simoun is waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:44.76,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:51.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll make them pay for\Ntaking my big sister hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:58.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,If our feelings go to pieces\Nagain, I couldn't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and I are alike\Nin one way... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind. What matters is\Nthat I'm Neviril's pair from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,One second is enough. Right the ship.\NWe're launching the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rubor and Caput were destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will be going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:37.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that? Keep the ship\Nlevel while Chor Tempest takes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:41.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll launch a simultaneous\Ncounterattack. There's no time to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blast away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, the fuselage Amuria and I shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're Sibylla Aurea's\Nauriga. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, our attacks\Naren't connecting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't hit\Nanything from that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're plunging in, Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll protect the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Diamond Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Diamond Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Diamond Ri Majon can\Nneutralize the enemy bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:44.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, it is one of the most difficult\Ndefensive Ri Majons to execute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:49.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors on this ship\Nare barely functioning anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only way is for\Nthem to convey us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave it to them.\NI'm sure Chor Tempest can manage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:05.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll hold the Diamond Ri Majon and\Nmove out of the enemy's firing range!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:50.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The hearing will be held this\Nafternoon, as soon as we arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:55.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to once more go over what\Nhappened with you, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:08.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You will see your father,\NLord Harukonf, at the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I are completely\Ndifferent in every respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're alike in just one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Neviril's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even if Neviril does come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what difference would that make?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when we finally\Ngot back to full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:38.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when I thought\Nwe could all fly together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one's blaming\Nyou anymore, Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like Dominüra\Nran off somewhere too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, don't you know where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if Neviril does come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:09:00.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's not as if we can\Ncarry on as Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll just disband\Nwith all members present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, here you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:13.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest sibyllae, it is almost\Ntime for the ceremony to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it\Nif you started getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:27.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing you did brought\Nabout the desired results?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:33.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's too early. I still believe that\NChor Tempest has vast potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,And two of the chor's\Nnew recruits, Rimone and Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:44.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...possess latent talents\Nunlike any sibylla before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sibylla in your report,\Nyour favorite, Rimone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:54.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,True, Harukonf-sama's prodding\Nadded two more sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Mamina and\NSibylla Yun, to Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:09:59.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,But no matter how\Nconvincing you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...everything will be\Ndecided soon in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:13.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, it would\Nbe wise to switch to our next plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:19.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it was you who allowed the highland\Nagents to board the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra, this discussion is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:06.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I only have your\Nbest interests in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,And your own too, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is true Chor Tempest's record\Nis nothing short of dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:19.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the sibyllae have\Ndestroyed it with their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,For Tempus Spatium's priestesses to\Nfeud and go at each other's throats...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...asserting themselves by baring\Ntheir basest instincts, is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:32.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,But what of our responsibility for\Nnot recognizing the conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a sham, allowing Plumbum\Nto carry out its destructive plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest saved our precious\NArcus Prima from the enemy's ruse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Had it not been for\Ntheir excellence that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't be\Nstanding here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one granted permission\Nto speak, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:04.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, that day at the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I did indeed hear\NElly's wail of anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:49.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please say what you\Nhave to say to everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:57.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are all priestesses serving\NTempus Spatium, and as sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we've listened to the Simouns and\Ndrawn Ri Majons across the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:07.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we have also killed scores of\Nsoldiers from neighboring countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...attempting to invade\NSimulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we carried out could\Nalmost be called slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,We met a massive fleet of aircraft\Nfrom Shoukoku, and in the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:28.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a battle.\NHow dare a sybilla speak like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:33.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have already lost three\Nof our beloved comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:38.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for Chor Caput, eleven of\Ntheir sibyllae have fallen in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:45.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the highland priestesses\Ngave their lives in the plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to destroy the Arcus Prima,\Neven more lives were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:53.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,There was no deceit in\Ntheir devotion to their god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,As priestesses ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what are we supposed to believe,\Nand how should we act?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are waging war now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are gathered here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...because we must sadly bid farewell\Nto a number of our beloved friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:22.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,We traveled together and fought side\Nby side with these comrades of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:27.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even for a time\Nof war, their departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,This was our original job, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,To offer flawless\NRi Majons to Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:39.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll return to our\Nnormal sibylla duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you really wanted to mourn\Nthe dead? That's pretty gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:51.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, that's not what I meant to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:57.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the last Ri Majon we'll ever do\Nas Chor Tempest. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we're really\Nqualified to mourn the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Qualified or not, it's duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:09.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just want to get\Nthis over with. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta,\Nplease begin the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:19.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to commemorate those who gave\Ntheir precious lives for their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:23.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.\NWe'll offer the Ri Majon of the Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:28.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am not looking to blame\Nanyone for this war we're waging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:32.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how tragic and painful it\Nis now, I believe it was meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:36.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether or not that is\NTempus Spatium's will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes no difference to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer even care whether\Nit's God's will anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, I do have\None question for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:57.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite all this, can I still\Ncall myself a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:07.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as you yourself wish it,\Nyou may still consider yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait! You made a comment\Nwe simply can't overlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:32.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't allow you to get away with\Nsaying you don't care about God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have something to say to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:45.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're from Chor Rubor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,My name is Vura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I summoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, how dare\Nyou take such a liberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:57.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it that you\Nhave to say? Sibylla Vura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...speak now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:11.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the chor all Simoun\Nsibyllae worship and take pride in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the finest chor of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,On behalf of all Simoun sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:20.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I beg you to consider\Npreserving Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:25.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you mean\NChor Tempest as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:29.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or Chor Tempest as\Na squadron of warriors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:35.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say you want us to preserve\NChor Tempest, but which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Twelve sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who become each other's pairs\Nand draw Ri Majons across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:45.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is only one Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that a new type of cannon?\NBut I'm sure we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:37.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are no cannons. They're\Nheaded straight for the great temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll disengage from the Ri Majon\Nand shoot those things down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:18.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everybody's always ganging up\Non us and making us suffer like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This must be our fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,One way or another,\Nwe're bound to do Ri Majons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can there be so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:53.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only the Iron Ri Majon\Ncan destroy a fleet that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:58.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't. It takes all six Simouns\Nto perform the Iron Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Iron Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:43.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a lovely breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've come home, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have good news. They won't\Ndisband Chor Tempest after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Goody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:12.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. This means we can fly\Nour Simouns across the skies again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:16.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad, Para-sama.\NWe'll be flying together again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world\Nhappened down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:24.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something must've\Nhappened, right? Neviril, Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that Chor Tempest\Nwon't be disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we must repair\Nthe Arcus Prima at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:43.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to move on to\Nthe next phase of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't lose face in the high council.\NChor Tempest can't go on as it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:01.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until the repairs on\Nthe Arcus Prima are completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we'll board the Messis and be\Ncharged with border reconnaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? We're boarding that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable. You should\Njust be thankful Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's right.\NThat old boat should do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:47.92,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:52.16,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:59.19,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.68,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:24.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:28.86,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:32.83,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:38.77,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:44.31,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.75,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:53.42,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:59.58,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.59,Titles,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.64,0:24:12.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...boards the antiquated ship Messis\Nand is on its way to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:18.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Birds in a Cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:19.97,Titles,,0,0,0,,Birds in a Cage
